project/
├── bin/
│   └── cli.js          ← the executable (has #!/usr/bin/env node at top)
├── lib/
│   ├── daemon.js       ← the long-running background worker
│   ├── server.js       ← express app that serves GUI + API
│   └── ...
├── web/                ← the React/Vue frontend (separate build)
│   ├── src/
│   └── dist/           ← built output, served statically by express
├── package.json
└── index.js            ← entry: decides whether to start daemon or just CLI

=======================================================================================

lib/
├── daemon.js          ← orchestrator, the EventEmitter bus
│
├── fs/                ← anything touching the filesystem
│   ├── watcher.js     ← chokidar wrapper
│   ├── chunker.js     ← split file into chunks
│   └── hasher.js      ← hash a file or chunk
│
├── sync/              ← business logic: the rules of your app
│   ├── index.js       ← "when file added, chunk it, hash it, store it"
│   └── delta.js       ← diff local state vs peer state
│
├── network/           ← anything touching the network
│   ├── webrtc.js
│   └── signaling.js
│
└── db/                ← database access
    ├── index.js       ← opens SQLite connection
    ├── files.js       ← queries about files
    └── chunks.js      ← queries about chunks